high_descs: Cross the kitchen to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Move the knife from the left side of the sink to the counter directly in front of the sink.
Pick up the knife and move to stand in front of the coffee maker to the right of the sink.
Place the knife in the mug on the base of the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug with the knife in it from the coffee maker.
Carry the mug and knife to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug and knife in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Move the mug with the knife in it to the kitchen sink.

high_descs: You will walk right from an white table counter and patrol around it's left side. Narrow your path to the sink counter.
You will have to pick up the yellow handle knife laying on that counter.
Around the trail of the counter to your you will see an small coffee maker.
Plant the knife inside of the coffee mug inside it already.
You will have to grab the mug cup and the knife together and walk away from the coffee maker.
An turn left towards the microwave you will make and walk on board counter sink on you right.
At last you will need to place the mug and it's precious knife in the bottom of the sink well.
anns.task_desc: The robot will comb for the knife with introduce an coffee mug (matching color).

high_descs: Go right towards doorway, turn left.
Walk towards fridge, turn left, turn right.
Walk towards sink in front of window.
Grab knife out of sink.
Turn right, turn left with knife.
Grab coffee mug, place knife into mug.
Turn right, place mug with knife into sink for cleaning.
anns.task_desc: Grab knife, place into mug, place in sink for cleaning
